dct_title_s: A development map of Israel, 1948 - 1965 / prepared & drawn by CARTA, Jerusalem.
dct_description_sm: Locates industrial installations, agricultural and mining regions, shows roads, railroads, water conduits, and oil and gas pipelines, aforested areas, and compares statistics for 1948 and 1964. Industrial installations are shown pictorially. "All statistics given in round figures to December 1964."
